00:17:00,900 --> 00:17:04,200
 Then put the needs of this home

425
00:17:04,200 --> 00:17:05,600
 in your heart.

426
00:17:05,600 --> 00:17:08,800
 Then, based on the needs he knows,

427
00:17:08,800 --> 00:17:10,900
 based on the different people,

428
00:17:10,900 --> 00:17:14,400
 give different instructions.

429
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,600
 This is why

430
00:17:16,600 --> 00:17:18,600
 after following Paul,

431
00:17:18,600 --> 00:17:21,900
 there was a great experience.

432
00:17:21,900 --> 00:17:25,100
 In the church of Philippians,

433
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:27,200
 after he drove away the demons,

434
00:17:27,200 --> 00:17:30,200
 he was persecuted and imprisoned.

435
00:17:30,200 --> 00:17:32,200
 Throughout the whole process,

436
00:17:32,200 --> 00:17:34,200
 from beginning to end, he was persecuted.

437
00:17:34,200 --> 00:17:37,300
 How did Paul meet the Lord in prison?

438
00:17:37,300 --> 00:17:39,200
 The Lord knew.

