00:17:39,200 --> 00:17:44,700
 Today, I will first show you

440
00:17:44,700 --> 00:17:48,900
 Paul's attitude towards the Lord

441
00:17:48,900 --> 00:17:51,400
 in the "The Message of the New Life"

442
00:17:51,400 --> 00:17:53,700
 He said to the Lord,

443
00:17:53,700 --> 00:17:55,800
 "Lord,

444
00:17:55,800 --> 00:17:57,900
 I am your son.

445
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,400
 You must know

