00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:38,400
 Every year,

463
00:18:38,400 --> 00:18:40,800
 a shepherd would come with me.

464
00:18:40,800 --> 00:18:43,300
 Or a pair of shepherds would come with me.

465
00:18:43,300 --> 00:18:45,100
 After the shepherd,

466
00:18:45,100 --> 00:18:46,800
 the next would be the patriarch.

467
00:18:46,800 --> 00:18:48,500
 After the patriarch,

468
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:50,600
 the new life,

469
00:18:50,600 --> 00:18:52,600
 the "re-education of values" would come.

470
00:18:52,600 --> 00:18:54,000
 These people came out

471
00:18:54,000 --> 00:18:56,800
 and became members of the group.

