00:18:56,800 --> 00:18:59,800
 Can we divide into two groups?

473
00:18:59,800 --> 00:19:01,800
 Can we divide into four groups?

474
00:19:01,800 --> 00:19:04,400
 We kept dividing

475
00:19:04,400 --> 00:19:08,000
 until we had soldiers to use.

476
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,400
 Dear brothers and sisters,

477
00:19:09,400 --> 00:19:11,000
 the patriarchs were like this.

478
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:11,800
 Three groups.

479
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:12,800
 What happened?

480
00:19:12,800 --> 00:19:14,400
 We had three groups of leaders.

481
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:15,600
 We had a deputy leader.

482
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:17,000
 Then we had a team.

