00:19:17,000 --> 00:19:18,400
 One more thing,

484
00:19:18,400 --> 00:19:20,400
 the disciples.

485
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:23,100
 In the past,

486
00:19:23,100 --> 00:19:25,000
 we had this arrangement.

487
00:19:25,000 --> 00:19:28,000
 Every person in the three groups

488
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:31,000
 had two or three disciples

489
00:19:31,000 --> 00:19:32,600
 to preach for them.

490
00:19:32,600 --> 00:19:34,800
 After preaching, you would be the leader.

491
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:37,000
 What was the purpose of the disciples?

492
00:19:37,000 --> 00:19:42,600
 The purpose was to become members of the three groups.

493
00:19:42,600 --> 00:19:44,600
 After being members,

494
00:19:44,600 --> 00:19:46,400
 they would be on the team.

495
00:19:46,400 --> 00:19:48,000
 Then they would be deputy leaders.

496
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:49,600
 Then they would be leaders.

497
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,600
 The new life.

498
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:53,000
 You may ask,

499
00:19:53,000 --> 00:19:54,200
 "Why is that?"

500
00:19:54,200 --> 00:19:56,200
 Because it's very simple.

501
00:19:56,200 --> 00:19:58,600
 The disciples had experienced it.

502
00:19:58,600 --> 00:20:01,400
 In the past, we didn't have this arrangement.

503
00:20:01,400 --> 00:20:04,400
 What was the result?

504
00:20:04,400 --> 00:20:08,000
 Let's look at the 18th chapter of the Book of Genesis.

505
00:20:08,000 --> 00:20:12,200
 This chapter left a deep impression on me.

506
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:17,200
 It was around 32 years ago.

507
00:20:17,200 --> 00:20:21,200
 32 years ago, in 1992 or 1991,

508
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:25,200
 we decided to form a small group to lead the church.

509
00:20:25,200 --> 00:20:27,200
 The main reason was

510
00:20:27,200 --> 00:20:29,800
 that we had 100 disciples at the beginning.

511
00:20:29,800 --> 00:20:31,800
 In the second year, we had more than 200 disciples.

512
00:20:31,800 --> 00:20:34,400
 In the third year, we had 300 or 400 disciples.

513
00:20:34,400 --> 00:20:36,400
 But at that time,

514
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,600
 there were only two preachers.

515
00:20:37,600 --> 00:20:40,400
 How could we raise so many people?

516
00:20:40,400 --> 00:20:41,800
 Moreover,

517
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:44,000
 the people of the Holy See were very good at choosing.

518
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,600
 They would find a deputy leader.

519
00:20:45,600 --> 00:20:47,200
 They would find someone from the Hong Kong TV station,

520
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,800
 meaning the Hong Kong TV station,

521
00:20:48,800 --> 00:20:51,600
 who was the most helpful to us.

522
00:20:51,600 --> 00:20:53,000
 They would find him.

523
00:20:53,000 --> 00:20:56,800
 So I invited two preachers to find me.

524
00:20:56,800 --> 00:20:58,600
 I invited four preachers.

525
00:20:58,600 --> 00:21:00,400
 They found me again.

526
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:02,400
 The result was

527
00:21:02,400 --> 00:21:08,200
 exactly the same as Moses' experience.

528
00:21:08,200 --> 00:21:10,000
 His father told him,

529
00:21:10,000 --> 00:21:13,400
 "Moses, you can't do it like this.

530
00:21:13,400 --> 00:21:16,200
 One by one, they are lining up to find you,

531
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,400
 to break up the discipline.

532
00:21:18,400 --> 00:21:20,200
 What is the result?

533
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:22,600
 How many disciples do you have?

534
00:21:22,600 --> 00:21:24,400
 Two million.

535
00:21:24,400 --> 00:21:26,200
 You have to find thousands of people.

536
00:21:26,200 --> 00:21:27,600
 You have to line up.

537
00:21:27,600 --> 00:21:28,800
 Why do you have to line up?

538
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,600
 Because it's not your turn yet.

539
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,600
 Moses was the only one to be a deputy leader,

540
00:21:32,600 --> 00:21:34,200
 to arrange and break up the discipline.

541
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:36,600
 So he was lining up from morning to night.

542
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:39,400
 Moses had to be a deputy leader from morning to night,

543
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:42,000
 to do all kinds of different things.

544
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,600
 His father told him,

545
00:21:43,600 --> 00:21:47,400
 "The result of your doing this,

546
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:51,200
 first, you will burn out.

547
00:21:51,200 --> 00:21:55,000
 Second, the people will rush out.

548
00:21:55,000 --> 00:22:02,800
 Third, sooner or later, everyone will die out."

549
00:22:02,800 --> 00:22:04,800
 After I saw Moses,

550
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,800
 I had a very deep impression.

551
00:22:06,800 --> 00:22:10,800
 It was because of this that I reminded myself,

552
00:22:10,800 --> 00:22:12,600
 "So, Moses,

553
00:22:12,600 --> 00:22:17,000
 do you want to be the only one acting,

554
00:22:17,000 --> 00:22:19,400
 and the rest of the people watching,

555
00:22:19,400 --> 00:22:20,600
 and the result of your doing this,

556
00:22:20,600 --> 00:22:22,400
 you will burn out,

557
00:22:22,400 --> 00:22:25,600
 and the rest of the people will rush out?

558
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:27,200
 In the end,

559
00:22:27,200 --> 00:22:28,600
 all the people in the assembly,

560
00:22:28,600 --> 00:22:29,600
 including you,

561
00:22:29,600 --> 00:22:32,400
 will all die out?"

562
00:22:32,400 --> 00:22:34,600
 I was in agony.

563
00:22:34,600 --> 00:22:38,000
 I decided to do one thing.

564
00:22:38,000 --> 00:22:43,600
 I decided to group up the whole church.

